PN,38101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FHigher-earning patients in Jersey
OL,8,Fcould have to pay for part of their
OL,9,Foff-island care as part of proposals
OL,10,Fto change what costs are covered by
OL,11,Fthe government.
OL,13,FReforms include means-testing for
OL,14,Fpatients travelling to the UK for non-
OL,15,Femergency treatment, and in Jersey,
OL,16,Fcharging all patients who stay in
OL,17,Fhospital when medically fit to leave
OL,18,Fand having been offered a care package.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe Health Minister, Deputy Tom Binet,
OL,8,Fsays: "Somebody has to pay for all
OL,9,Fthese treatments, and we have ignored
OL,10,Fthat fact, in my view, for far too
OL,11,Flong.
OL,13,F"The whole idea is to have enough
OL,14,Fmoney in to shorten the waiting lists,
OL,15,Fto have a better, more reliable
OL,16,Fservice.
OL,18,F"I think we need a more graduated
OL,19,Fsystem, with obviously wealthier
OL,20,Fpeople paying the most."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FIt comes as Deputy Tom Binet has
OL,8,Fpresented a draft report to the Health
OL,9,Fand Care Board, which could change
OL,10,Fpolicies such as the publicly funded
OL,11,Fhealthcare eligibility, off-island
OL,12,Ftravel and accommodation policies, and
OL,13,Fthe rules on discharge-ready patients
OL,14,Fremaining in hospital.
OL,16,FThe Board will review and provide
OL,17,Fcomments on the items to further
OL,18,Finform the Minister for Health and
OL,19,FSocial Services in determining any
OL,20,Famendments and how best to implement
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe draft reintroduces the pre-2017
OL,8,Fpolicy of eligibility testing based on
OL,9,Fhousehold income.
OL,11,FIn the report, the Health Minister
OL,12,Fexplains: "Healthcare costs are
OL,13,Frising, and Health Care Jersey (HCJ)
OL,14,Fmust ensure that finite public funding
OL,15,Fis used fairly and directed to the
OL,16,FIslanders who need care."
OL,18,FAlso, outlined within the proposals
OL,19,Fare the potential risks that follow
OL,20,Fthe reforms:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FDeputy Binet warns of the consequences
OL,8,Fwithout the reforms, he says: "Off-
OL,9,Fisland travel and accommodation costs
OL,10,Fwill continue to exceed budget (due to
OL,11,Frise in costs and rise in UK
OL,12,Freferrals), requiring other healthcare
OL,13,Fservices to be cut.
OL,15,F"Delays that arise when discharge-
OL,16,Fready patients choose to remain in the
OL,17,Fhospital will continue to reduce bed
OL,18,Fcapacity, resulting in non-admission
OL,19,Fof other patients awaiting treatment
OL,20,Fand extending waits for elective care."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FHow much could islanders be paying?
OL,9,FFor non-emergency treatment, there
OL,10,Fwould be four different levels of
OL,11,Fsupport:
OL,13,FIf you are a single adult and earn up
OL,14,Fto #48,100, and #112,800 if a family,
OL,15,Fyou can get funding for accommodation,
OL,16,Ftravel to the UK and travel within the
OL,17,FUK.JGroup B:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FAny adult earning up to #58,700 or
OL,8,F#138,400 for a family would be
OL,9,Feligible for accommodation travel to
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FGroup C:JHouseholds earning up to
OL,13,F#210,400 would receive payment towards
OL,14,Faccommodation only.
OL,16,FAny household earning more than
OL,17,F#210,400 would receive no support
OL,18,Ftowards any travel or accommodation.
OL,20,FPublicly funded healthcare eligibility
OL,21,Fpolicy:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FCurrently, emergency care is free to
OL,8,Faccess for all residents and visitors
OL,9,Fto Jersey, with access to free non-
OL,10,Femergency care based on length of
OL,11,Fresidency and economic contribution to
OL,12,Fthe island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe reforms would see visitors pay for
OL,8,Fall emergency care unless they have
OL,9,Fmade a significant social or economic
OL,10,Fcontribution to the island or are from
OL,11,Fthe UK or another jurisdiction with a
OL,12,FReciprocal Healthcare Agreement, which
OL,13,Fallows citizens from one country to
OL,14,Faccess necessary, often free or
OL,15,Freduced-cost, state-provided medical
OL,16,Ftreatment while visiting another
OL,17,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FResidents who have moved to Jersey but
OL,8,Fare not working will be required to
OL,9,Fpay for emergency care until they have
OL,10,Fcompleted 12 consecutive months of
OL,11,Fresidency.
OL,13,FWorking residents who do not hold a
OL,14,F"Licensed" status or a "Temporary Work
OL,15,FPermit" must pay for emergency care
OL,16,Funtil they have been working on the
OL,17,Fisland for at least 6 months.
OL,19,FDischarge-ready patients remaining in
OL,20,Fhospital:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe draft also proposes that patients
OL,8,Fwill be charged if they are medically
OL,9,Ffit and choose to continue receiving
OL,10,Fcare in a hospital after a care
OL,11,Fpackage outside the hospital has been
OL,12,Farranged.
OL,14,FThe charges are:
OL,16,F#965 a day for the daily cost of
OL,17,Foccupying a private patient bed for
OL,18,Flong-term care services.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,F#450 a day for occupying an acute bed
OL,8,Fon a shared ward for long-term care
OL,9,Fservices or part thereof.
OL,11,F#650 a day for using a private room
OL,12,Ffor long-term care services on a
OL,13,Fshared ward or part thereof.
OL,15,FThe purpose of the charge would be to
OL,16,Fimprove bed capacity and to treat more
OL,17,Fpatients.
OL,19,FOff-island travel and accommodation
OL,20,Fpolicy:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FIf approved, 30% of public patients
OL,8,Fwould not receive fully funded
OL,9,Foverseas travel and accommodation.
OL,11,FHigher-income households would need to
OL,12,Fpay for part or all of their travel or
OL,13,Faccommodation.
OL,15,FTreatment would remain fully funded
OL,16,Ffor eligible public patients.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FThe report adds: "This policy does not
OL,8,Fcreate new charges; it restricts
OL,9,Faccess to a discretionary benefit for
OL,10,Fa limited group of patients from
OL,11,Fhigher-income households."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FDefending the proposals, the Health
OL,8,FMinister Deputy Tom Binet argues:
OL,9,F"This is a difficult one, a lot of
OL,10,Fpeople have paid into a tax system
OL,11,Ftheir whole lives, that is great, but
OL,12,FI think we should have looked at
OL,13,Fhealth funding a lot earlier, because
OL,14,Fyou cannot carry on getting more and
OL,15,Fmore health services on the same
OL,16,Fbudget.
OL,18,F"This is just the beginning of a
OL,19,Fprocess, looking at the very difficult
OL,20,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,F"There are lots of ailments that are
OL,8,Fdeeply unpleasant, cancer being one of
OL,9,Fthem. This isn't really about
OL,10,Fdifferentiating by type of illness, it
OL,11,Fis probably about differentiating
OL,12,Fincome, and I think at somepoint in
OL,13,Ftime we may have to consider
OL,14,Fintroducing some sort of graduated
OL,15,Fpayment scheme.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FHe adds, there is no definite amount
OL,8,Fthis system would save the health
OL,9,Fdepartment, he explains: "It won't be
OL,10,Fa fortune, I haven't got the figure
OL,11,Foff the top of my head, and it won't
OL,12,Fbe a great deal, so this is the start
OL,13,Fof the process and it has to run a lot
OL,14,Fwider than just introducing small
OL,15,Findividual charges.
OL,17,F"This is just about taking these
OL,18,Fchanges to the health advisory board
OL,19,Fto gauge their opinions on it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G17/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FAnswering how different illnesses will
OL,8,Fbe categorised, Deputy Binet explains:
OL,9,F"I am sure when we come up with this,
OL,10,Fwe are going to have some exceptions
OL,11,Ffor various circumstances, and if it's
OL,12,Fgraduated, that shouldn't be too much
OL,13,Fof a problem.
OL,15,F"The whole idea is to have enough
OL,16,Fmoney in to shorten the waiting lists,
OL,17,Fto have a better, more reliable
OL,18,Fservice.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G18/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,F"I think we need a more graduated
OL,8,Fsystem, with obviously wealthier
OL,9,Fpeople paying the most."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Health and Social Care
OL,12,Fsays: "Under the draft proposals, all
OL,13,Fpatients under 18 would be exempt. For
OL,14,Findividuals who travel frequently,
OL,15,Fthere would be an option to apply for
OL,16,Fsupport on a discretionary basis.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G19/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,F"Please note that cancer patients were
OL,8,Fincluded in the previous 2017
OL,9,Fmeanstested scheme, which did not
OL,10,Fprovide any conditionspecific
OL,11,Fexemptions. Under the updated
OL,12,Fapproach, eligibility thresholds would
OL,13,Fbe determined solely by annual income
OL,14,Fas assessed by Revenue Jersey, with no
OL,15,Fconsideration of assets."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G20/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38121
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FCommenting on the reforms, Vice Chair
OL,8,Fof the Health and Social Security
OL,9,FPanel, Deputy Jonathan Renouf, says:
OL,10,F"I think there are some serious
OL,11,Fquestions to ask about the criteria
OL,12,Ffor charging people.
OL,14,F"It says it will be when there has
OL,15,Fbeen a suitable care package
OL,16,Fidentified, and if you don't take the
OL,17,Fcare package, you have to leave the
OL,18,Fhospital or pay.
OL,20,F"But who determines what a suitable
OL,21,Fcare package is?"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G21/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
