FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38122
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FFormer patient, Sean Le Scelleur, had
OL,8,Fa heart attack in April and had to
OL,9,Fspend 30 days in the intensive care
OL,10,Funit in Jersey before being sent to
OL,11,Fthe Oxford John Radcliffe Hospital,
OL,12,Fwhere he spent a further four weeks.
OL,14,FHe explains: "I had a quadruple heart
OL,15,Fbypass, together with other ongoing
OL,16,Fissues. During this, I had my wife and
OL,17,Fdaughter come over at separate times.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G22/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38123
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,F"The total costs associated with
OL,8,Fflying them over and keeping them in
OL,9,Fhotels, food and accomodation was over
OL,10,F#6,000. None of which was refunded;
OL,11,Fthere was no offer from the States of
OL,12,FJersey at all.
OL,14,F"It is frustrating and unsettling for
OL,15,Fthose individuals who are going
OL,16,Fthrough the treatment process at the
OL,17,Fmoment, because the goal post keeps
OL,18,Fcontinually changing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G23/24
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
