OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1771883476
OL,3,CCould the richest third in Jersey soon
OL,4,Chave to pay for some treatment in the
OL,5,CUK?
OL,7,FHe adds: "It is another goal post and
OL,8,FI don't think people, certainly not
OL,9,Fmyself, would have ever budgeted for
OL,10,Fthis.
OL,12,F"It's heartless."
